attributes.Long form description: The student is preparing their GoPro for use. They change the SD card and turn on the camera. Then, they attach it to their belt in tripod mode. Next, they change it to handheld mode and finally disassemble it.

attributes.Transcription: Hello, welcome to our sudy and thank you for taking part.
In front of you, you will see a GoPro action camera we'll be using it for this task.
First, please change the battery in the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the battery of the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: You will find the battery compartment on the right side of the camera.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: To open it, please pull on the notch on the bottom of the camera.

attributes.Transcription: To open it, please pull on the notch on the bottom of the camera.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student tries to pull the notch.
The student tries to open the battery top pulling at the top.
The student tries to open the battery door pulling the top.
The student should push the notch, instead of that, he open the battery door.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please change the micro SD card in the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student changes their micro SD card.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please turn on the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns on the camera.

attributes.Transcription: To stop recording the currecnt recording and turn on the camera using the button on the left.
Next, please turn off the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns off their GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Turn off the camera, please long press the button on the left.
Next, please put on the strap mount on the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student mounts the GoPro into the belt.

attributes.Transcription: To put the strap on the camera, please first unscrew.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should place the gopro into the belt and after screw it on with the lock screw.

attributes.Transcription: Please first slide the GoPro into the mount.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student tried to moun the gopro moun to the belt.
The student can't insert correctly the lock screw.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please change the mount on the GoPro from the shoulder strap mount to the tripod.

attributes.Action sentence: The student changes to the tripod mode.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student couldn't insert the gorpo into the tripod.
The student tried to insert the lock screw.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please change the mount from the tripod mount to the handle mount

attributes.Action sentence: The student changes to the handheld mode.

attributes.Transcription: Lastly, please, remove the gopro from the handheld mode.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the GoPro from the handheld mode.

attributes.Transcription: That will be the end of this task, you may now press the stop button.
